text: Jónas Ásgeirsson (25 August 1920 - 14 June 1996) was an Icelandic ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Icelandic male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Iceland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics
